%N A396964 Decimal expansion of (-1)*Integral_{x=0..1} log(-log(x))/(1 + x^2 + 2*x*cos(4)) dx.
%H A396964 Robert Reynolds, <a href="https://arxiv.org/abs/2412.10395">Derivation of some definite integrals</a>, arXiv:2412.10395 [math.GM], 2024-2025, page 10, eq. 4.11.
%F A396964 Equals (1/2)*Pi*csc(4)*log((2*Pi)^(2 - 4/Pi)*Gamma(3/2 - 2/Pi)/Gamma(-1/2 + 2/Pi)).
